reviewText: Given as a Gift to our Son, as he is a HUGE DALLAS COWBOY FAN.  He really enjoyed it.
Very well produced films about two very different personalities but yet successful coaches who in their own way will forever be admired by Cowboy fans.
Great DVD for any Cowboys fan!
Great DVD to have for any Cowboys fan
This is a good comparision between to coaching styles, personalities and players eras.  They both won Super Bowls and made "men" of their players.
I'm a long time fan of the Dallas cowboys also it was a good deal to  get both at one time
